oken tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>body</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>p</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>我见<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>b</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>青山<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>b</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>多<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>b</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>妩媚<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>b</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>,青山<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>b</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>见我<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>b</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>应<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>b</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>如是<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>b</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>。<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>p</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>I</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>倾斜<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>I</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>p</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>s</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>删除线<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>s</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>p</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>u</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>下划线<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>u</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>div</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>我的是div 我独占一行<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>span</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>熊出没，<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span> <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>span</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>喜羊羊，<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span> <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>span</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>猪猪侠，<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p><img src="2.jpg" alt="文本格式化"></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
